
                   INSTALL

1  Installation instructioins
   
   In the vostok/ directory created after extracting the tarball simply run
   the provided install.sh script. This script will copy the required files
   to /opt/vostok.
   
   After the installation process is finished you should add the directory 
   /opt/vostok/bin to your path.
   Afterwards you can use vpm to install cartridges. Some cartridges will be
   provided by Makara on www.makara.com